data.title: Bitcoin Price Could Hit $170K — But Strategy ‘Resilience’ Is Vital: JPMorgan
data.description: JPMorgan analysts say the near-term direction of Bitcoin’s price now depends less on miner behavior and more on the financial resilience of Strategy, the world’s largest corporate holder of Bitcoin, even as mining pressure and market volatility persist.In a report led by managing director Nikolaos Panigirtzoglou, the bank identified two ...
